  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS, improved OTIF, accelerated payback, and optimized logistics infrastructure investments.]
  N5 -->|Insufficient budget for all high-prio...| B1[Defer lower-priority investments and reallocate funds.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Adjusted budget allocation to focus on critical investments.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Significant variance in ROI analysis ...| B2[Conduct additional analysis and consult with experts.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Revised investment strategy based on further insights.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N5 -->|Unexpected changes in supply network ...| B3[Re-evaluate capacity investments and adjust plans accordingly.]
